name: Last kiss in cold wind night
description:
Cold. Night.

Snow. White.


It's dark outside.


Last night. We had.

Our last - Goodbye.


Asked for a hug.

Got broken heart.


No words.

No cry.


Stay up all night.


Just messaged - Why?

Got whispered - Bye...


  • Elle Hex


Like it, if You Like it =)
